507a92db-634d-493b-b2d0-7249e0beac7d.title: Head Mourner
507a92db-634d-493b-b2d0-7249e0beac7d.text:
How did you get into West Ardougne? Ah well you'll
have to stay, can't risk you spreading the plague
outside.

options.text: I haven't got the plague though...
I'm looking for a woman named Elena.

b1bdfa4a-cba5-4f35-b6be-d648f4f01ad5.title: Head Mourner
b1bdfa4a-cba5-4f35-b6be-d648f4f01ad5.text:
We're working for King Lathas of East Ardougne. He
has tasked us with containing the accursed plague
sweeping West Ardougne.

790b6cbb-339d-47cf-9db8-b8f06d67d81d.title: Head Mourner
790b6cbb-339d-47cf-9db8-b8f06d67d81d.text:
We also do our best to ease these people's suffering.
We're nicknamed mourners because we spend a lot of
time at plague victim funerals, no one else is allowed to
risk attending.

d2df987f-a4c1-47a8-9750-32b2ea4d33b5.title: Head Mourner
d2df987f-a4c1-47a8-9750-32b2ea4d33b5.text:
It's a demanding job, and we get little thanks from the
people here.

5ce2bfe3-a4ad-433d-a644-f0a3bb031a6f.title: Note
5ce2bfe3-a4ad-433d-a644-f0a3bb031a6f.text:
mourner in black clothes, behind the townhall,
holding a vial.

3f6d9e4b-5b5f-48f0-bb9b-e719f7e2482c.title: <player>
3f6d9e4b-5b5f-48f0-bb9b-e719f7e2482c.text: I haven't got the plague though...

5260f8b3-1a39-44f6-8dd0-2f9896ea26f9.title: Head Mourner
5260f8b3-1a39-44f6-8dd0-2f9896ea26f9.text:
Can't risk you being a carrier. That protective clothing
you have isn't regulation issue. It won't meet safety
standards.

4c6f1b25-7c2b-439d-abd3-3878604f0d73.title: <player>
4c6f1b25-7c2b-439d-abd3-3878604f0d73.text: I'm looking for a woman named Elena.

65c9b0bb-88ee-41ae-9d7e-749970a584d2.title: Head Mourner
65c9b0bb-88ee-41ae-9d7e-749970a584d2.text:
Ah yes, I've heard of her. A healer I believe. She must
be mad coming over here voluntarily.

404c2eb2-d65f-4199-a42a-598a324a9aef.title: Head Mourner
404c2eb2-d65f-4199-a42a-598a324a9aef.text:
I hear rumours she has probably caught the plague
now. Very tragic, a stupid waste of life.

06bc3c6c-1191-4abf-bb3a-7d8d8b963f10.title: Head Mourner
06bc3c6c-1191-4abf-bb3a-7d8d8b963f10.text:
How did you get into West Ardougne? Ah well you'll
have to stay, can't risk you spreading the plague
outside.

options.text: I need clearance to enter a plague house.
I haven't got the plague though...
I'm looking for a woman named Elena.

b2d44102-fea2-48fb-88a2-98f36e29a95f.title: <player>
b2d44102-fea2-48fb-88a2-98f36e29a95f.text:
I need clearance to enter a plague house. It's in the
south east corner of West Ardougne.

ae27d21f-3b77-477c-9ba1-2eef3b8a4b43.title: Head Mourner
ae27d21f-3b77-477c-9ba1-2eef3b8a4b43.text: You must be nuts, absolutely not!

options.text: I've got a gas mask though...

fc39f7f4-0c55-4fff-ba59-95d00f50101e.title: Head Mourner
fc39f7f4-0c55-4fff-ba59-95d00f50101e.text: You're wasting my time, I have a lot of work to do!

e57e03da-d55b-4ba5-93e6-c59509a59da0.title: <player>
e57e03da-d55b-4ba5-93e6-c59509a59da0.text: I've got a gas mask though...

014e72b9-0b31-4a02-9771-0d5e0a371955.title: Head Mourner
014e72b9-0b31-4a02-9771-0d5e0a371955.text:
It's not regulation. Anyway you're not properly trained
to deal with the plague.

e2a85a46-266e-4058-8f88-b085d69bc063.title: Head Mourner
e2a85a46-266e-4058-8f88-b085d69bc063.text: It requires a strict 18 months of training.

ce2d0c03-166e-4bd7-bacf-5289f6f2f762.title: <player>
ce2d0c03-166e-4bd7-bacf-5289f6f2f762.text: I don't have that sort of time.

8ca67a0e-e067-491d-aee8-f6c545b22f06.title: Head Mourner
8ca67a0e-e067-491d-aee8-f6c545b22f06.text:
Well they're as good as dead then, no point in trying to
save them.

adf8ca4c-8a4e-4c5e-ab4e-677d66b33d6f.title: Note
adf8ca4c-8a4e-4c5e-ab4e-677d66b33d6f.text:
find another way,
this step can be skipped by going straight to town hall.

4d568d9f-1811-4190-97d8-494524592897.title: Head Mourner
4d568d9f-1811-4190-97d8-494524592897.text:
How did you get into West Ardougne? Ah well you'll
have to stay, can't risk you spreading the plague
outside.

options.text: I haven't got the plague though...
